529
00:39:50,914 --> 00:39:54,300
Girls today are smart when it comes to love.

530
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:58,000
The love is as deep as the boy's pockets!

531
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:01,800
Malika's not like that, my dear.

532
00:40:01,800 --> 00:40:03,911
That's where you're wrong, my friend.

533
00:40:03,911 --> 00:40:06,393
She hasn't the foggiest.

534
00:40:06,393 --> 00:40:07,690
Oh?

535
00:40:07,690 --> 00:40:11,690
