536
00:40:11,690 --> 00:40:13,916
Absolutely.
-Absolutely.

537
00:40:14,370 --> 00:40:19,936
Love is blind to status, mate.

538
00:40:19,936 --> 00:40:24,770
Well, in that case, go and tell her who you are.

539
00:40:32,200 --> 00:40:34,746
Don't even think about it!

540
00:40:34,746 --> 00:40:38,907
We're just kidding. You took it too seriously!

541
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:41,566
Mate...

542
00:40:42,116 --> 00:40:45,009
I think you're right...

543
00:40:45,537 --> 00:40:48,220
I should tell Malika the truth.

544
00:40:48,220 --> 00:40:51,207
No way, mate. Please. Don't.

545
00:40:51,207 --> 00:40:53,578
You're mad when it comes to love.

546
00:40:53,578 --> 00:40:56,548
She can take it,

547
00:40:56,548 --> 00:40:58,959
But you can't.

548
00:41:00,348 --> 00:41:02,720
3, 2, 1...

549
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:14,690
♪ <i>I'm longing for your love but you are moving away</i> ♪

