553
00:41:49,036 --> 00:41:52,830
So my company bores you!

554
00:41:52,830 --> 00:41:54,896
No way, mate.

555
00:41:54,896 --> 00:41:56,206
Anyway...

556
00:41:56,206 --> 00:42:02,926
When are you taking me to your place?

557
00:42:06,730 --> 00:42:08,876
Tell me.

558
00:42:09,316 --> 00:42:10,916
Malika...

559
00:42:12,450 --> 00:42:14,606
Oh, muck...
-Oh my God...

560
00:42:14,606 --> 00:42:16,436
What'd you do, Noriyan?

561
00:42:16,436 --> 00:42:20,225
He's coming, Noriyan...
-Relax.

562
00:42:23,820 --> 00:42:27,751
Think you'd show it off to your girlfriend?
-Mind your tongue.

563
00:42:27,751 --> 00:42:32,001
