-No, Noriyan!

564
00:42:32,001 --> 00:42:34,955
I'm leaving if you got out.

565
00:42:34,955 --> 00:42:37,470
Please get going!
-Hello!

566
00:42:37,470 --> 00:42:39,100
You coming?

567
00:42:39,100 --> 00:42:41,381
Can you wait until I park it?

568
00:42:41,381 --> 00:42:42,540
I'm coming.

569
00:42:42,540 --> 00:42:44,420
Go park.

570
00:42:55,190 --> 00:42:57,550
What were you thinking?

571
00:42:57,550 --> 00:43:02,600
Were you just going to fight him like a chav?

572
00:43:02,600 --> 00:43:06,996
As if you've got a shortage of cars!

573
00:43:06,996 --> 00:43:10,227
If I don't, it doesn't mean I can go about ramming random cars on the road!

574
00:43:10,227 --> 00:43:12,488
Can't you look where you're going?

